        <mxCell id="cF_lEN3bx5_BOaXpCxlm-12" parent="1" style="rounded=0;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#f8cecc;strokeColor=#b85450;" value="&lt;font&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-weight: bold;&quot;&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 20px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);&quot;&gt;Regarding LLMs and SuperCodex compatibility:&lt;/font&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;font&gt;There is a high likelyhood that some LLMs are not going to be compatibile with SuperCodex due to&amp;nbsp;&lt;u style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);&quot;&gt;weight calculation collapse&lt;/u&gt; during IDR and ST.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;color: rgb(75, 37, 139);&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;I am currently trying to resolve&amp;nbsp;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;color: rgb(75, 37, 139);&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;compatibility&amp;nbsp;by introducing RAG in IDR and ST.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;The theory is that the target technology documentation was poorly introduced in the training dataset.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;Programming IDR and ST to check against technology documentation might resolve the&amp;nbsp;&lt;u style=&quot;&quot;&gt;weight calculation collapse&lt;/u&gt;.&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;Until conclusion is arrived at it&#39;s possible that some LLMs simply won&#39;t work due to how they were trained.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;The LLM training mistakes/incompatiblity causes have yet to be determined.&lt;br&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;color: rgb(255, 0, 0);&quot;&gt;&lt;b style=&quot;&quot;&gt;Trying to train and or fine-tune LLMs for compatibility with SuperCodex is considered out of scope for this project and should not be considered as a possible solution.&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;b&gt;LLMs that work fine during IDR and ST:&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 102, 0);&quot;&gt;&lt;b style=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#006600&quot;&gt;GPT&lt;/font&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 204);&quot;&gt;(Enterprise - General WebUI - Paid)&lt;/font&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 102, 0);&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;Gemini&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent;&quot;&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 204), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;(&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 204);&quot;&gt;Enterprise - General&amp;nbsp;WebUI - Free&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent;&quot;&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 204), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;)&lt;/font&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;b&gt;LLMs that produce errors due&amp;nbsp;&lt;u&gt;weight calculation collapse&lt;/u&gt;&amp;nbsp;during IDR and ST:&lt;br&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;color: rgb(153, 0, 0);&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;Grok&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent;&quot;&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 204), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;(&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 204);&quot;&gt;Enterprise -&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 204); background-color: transparent;&quot;&gt;General&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 204); background-color: transparent;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 204);&quot;&gt;WebUI - Free&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 204), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;)&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;color: rgb(153, 0, 0);&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;Gemma&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/font&gt; &lt;font style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 204);&quot;&gt;(Local)&lt;/font&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="600" width="290" x="-2440" y="-3000" as="geometry" />
